# Input

```scss
@mixin boundary{/* leading */ $color /* name */ :/* value */red/* trailing */!default /* modifier */ ;$plain:/* value */red/* trailing */ ;}
@mixin root-dedent{$break /* name */
:red;$line // name
:red;}
$tight/* name */:red;
/* gap */

$gap:red;
$line:red!default // c
;
$plain-trailing:red;// c

```


# Formatted

```scss
@mixin boundary {
	/* leading */
	$color/* name */ : /* value */ red /* trailing */ !default /* modifier */ ;
	$plain: /* value */ red /* trailing */;
}
@mixin root-dedent {
	$break/* name */
: red;
	$line // name
: red;
}
$tight/* name */: red;
/* gap */

$gap: red;
$line: red !default; // c
$plain-trailing: red; // c

```
